Class OpenMetadataPropertyConverterBase

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.converters.OpenMetadataPropertyConverterBase
Direct Known Subclasses:
OpenMetadataConverterBase
public class OpenMetadataPropertyConverterBase extends Object
OpenMetadataPropertyConverterBase provides the methods for converting each of the Open Metadata properties from an element property value to a bean property.
